values:
I've found I am rooming with Dearka, and Nicol Amarfi. At least one of the faces is familiar.

About being here, of course, my family name is Jule, so I'm to be expected to graduate with top marks. There doesn't seem to be many others around who seem to hold any competition; but we'll see, I'll leave here wearing red no matter what it takes.

Other than that, I don't know what else to type.
